text:
@AISafetyMemes @NPCollapse We really don’t. Intuition is linear. 

That said, I’ve seen exponentials become logarithmic (S-curve) so many times in AI. 

Progress seems to be a series of overlapping log curves that cumulatively generate an exponential.

